raw_text:
Visit the website and click on the "Important Link" on the right side to 
first download the JRE, then the PKI Component (32/64 bit), based on 
your system. Be patient during the installation process of both the JRE 
and PKI Component. 
 
1) JRE Installation 
Open the link https://www.openlogic.com/openjdk-downloads  
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
Find the below steps for installing JRE 8 32/64 according to your system. 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
During the JRE installation, select 'Entire feature will be installed on the local 
hard drive” in all drives. 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
2) PKI Component Installation. Extract the file and then installed 32/64 
according to your system.
